titles.title: Expressing the sense of the House of Representatives that the United States should initiate preparatory work to begin negotiations to enter into a free trade agreement with Tunisia.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary: 5/1/2015--Introduced. Expresses the sense of the House of Representatives that the United States should initiate preparatory work to begin negotiations to enter into a free trade agreement with Tunisia.
